{"tid":1430782,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"要醒既721都醒曬","createTime":"2019-08-07T23:30:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-08T11:00:14.000Z","uid":24721,"like":16,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"5544ff0966cc43a1ab6d1319ea36c6a9e5d95c7f","tid":1430782,"uid":24721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T23:30:56.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">未呀！</span><br />\n點解仲有人講呢句？<br />\n<br />\n輿論戰係持久戰<br />\n善忘派，無腦派同中間派係會彈左彈右<br />\n<br />\n經過8月5知道仲有班人根本新聞都唔睇係度屌<br />\n呢班人其實好有影響力，因為平時係示威旁邊屌既就係呢D，佢地只會靠口耳相傳但人數超多<br />\n<br />\n尋日仲要比狗轉移視線，帶風向<br />\n<br />\n時刻警醒呀！"},{"pid":"282ed4b8cf87134b53e0c37d80a99d2eddce32e0","tid":1430782,"uid":24721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T23:35:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f291638dcd695cb6efcc70fc09fdb6ff2996688","tid":1430782,"uid":24721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T23:41:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c2af9a6f5afa8b63d043bea5e1b939df72f1d86","tid":1430782,"uid":222190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T23:42:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hqGGNvq.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhqGGNvq.png&h=287dc689&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Kcq023L.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKcq023L.png&h=0796397d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/08/08/074223_ee9bd865176d0dc56b5be2ca89399833.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F08%2F08%2F07